## You're Leaving Money On The Table Every Single Day

Right now, your ideal patients are scrolling. They're looking for solutions. They have money to spend.

The problem? They have no idea you exist. Meanwhile, your competitors are winning — showing up in the feed, booking consults, scaling their practice.

## Meta Ads Done Right for Healthcare

Meta ads for healthcare require a very specific kind of expertise. Meta introduced new healthcare advertising restrictions in 2025 and is rolling out another wave in 2026 specifically targeting lead-generation campaigns medical practices depend on. **About 70% of healthcare ads get rejected** for policy violations.

We've spent years navigating this. We know what Meta approves, what it rejects, and how to structure campaigns that actually run.

## Our Approach

- **Compliance-first structure** — campaigns built to survive Meta's healthcare restrictions
- **Ideal-patient targeting** — not broad blasts, but laser-focused audience segments
- **Creative built for conversion** — single-image, carousel, and video ads tested against your actual patient economics
- **Lifetime value tracking** — measure ROI on real revenue, not just last-click attribution

## Case Study

One med spa achieved **4x ROAS** by measuring customer lifetime value instead of last-click. Read the full story: [Medical Spa Marketing ROI](/blog/medical-spa-marketing-roi-lifetime-value-case-study).

